        "Certificate of Undergraduate Study in Public Policy": [
            "Certificate of Undergraduate Study in Public Policy The Certificate of Undergraduate Study (CUGS) in Public Policy provides students with a fundamental understanding of critical tools for effective policy analysis, including formal program evaluation, cost-benefit analysis, and an introduction to policy-relevant statistics. The flexible course study enables students to take a range of courses (on health, labor, environmental, and social policies), preparing them for employment or graduate degree training."
        ],
